            </svg>
            Track coverage over time
          </h3>
          <p class="mb-3">View your recent commits and see how coverage evolves across your project. Filter by repository, branch and time.</p>
          <p class="text-muted">The dashboard provides a clear timeline of your pull requests, making it easy to find changes that could be worth revisiting and improving.</p>
        </div>
